260
00:18:18,312 --> 00:18:21,951
Hi, Sir. How can I help you?

261
00:18:21,951 --> 00:18:25,571
Sorry, Sir. You can't enter unless you've made an appointment.

262
00:18:25,571 --> 00:18:27,712
Why don't you wait in the waiting area?

263
00:18:27,712 --> 00:18:29,911
Our customer service manager will attend to you shortly.

264
00:18:29,911 --> 00:18:31,651
Sure.

265
00:18:37,172 --> 00:18:40,051
Hello, this is "Dear Wedding Boutique."

266
00:18:40,051 --> 00:18:41,811
Hello?

267
00:18:43,512 --> 00:18:45,291
Hello?

268
00:19:07,172 --> 00:19:09,631
Can you pull this ribbon for me?

269
00:19:35,712 --> 00:19:37,451
Thanks.

270
00:19:40,272 --> 00:19:42,331
Why are you here?

271
00:19:44,652 --> 00:19:46,811
I should be the one asking this question.

272
00:19:46,811 --> 00:19:49,191
Isn't this during office hours? Why are you here?

273
00:19:49,191 --> 00:19:51,071
- I took a day off.
- Did I approve your request for leave?

274
00:19:51,071 --> 00:19:53,971
Sir. Sir. Sorry.

275
00:19:53,971 --> 00:19:55,571
I'm the fiancé of Zhixia's mother.

276
00:19:55,571 --> 00:19:58,251
I asked Zhixia here to try the wedding gown on her mother's behalf.

277
00:19:58,251 --> 00:20:00,831
I didn't mean to disturb her work. I'm so sorry.

278
00:20:00,831 --> 00:20:03,671
- What?
- Zhixia's mother.

279
00:20:08,872 --> 00:20:10,691
