383
00:28:15,433 --> 00:28:17,293
You...

384
00:28:17,293 --> 00:28:19,373
Do you know me?

385
00:28:20,934 --> 00:28:23,113
Don't you remember who I am?

386
00:28:23,113 --> 00:28:24,713
Who is he?

387
00:28:26,094 --> 00:28:28,373
I guess he's still a little light-headed.

388
00:28:28,373 --> 00:28:30,493
