395
00:28:46,513 --> 00:28:48,053
Go ahead.

396
00:28:58,410 --> 00:29:00,473
Officer.

397
00:29:00,473 --> 00:29:05,593
Did you catch him committing a misdemeanor?

398
00:29:05,593 --> 00:29:07,314
Yes

399
00:29:07,314 --> 00:29:09,073
but not really.

400
00:29:09,073 --> 00:29:10,953
I didn't exactly catch him doing that,

401
00:29:10,953 --> 00:29:12,733
but your boyfriend...

402
00:29:12,733 --> 00:29:15,410
He wasn't my boyfriend,

403
00:29:15,410 --> 00:29:16,950
but I guess

404
00:29:16,950 --> 00:29:19,634
now he is.

405
00:29:19,634 --> 00:29:24,193
