409
00:29:30,913 --> 00:29:33,194
- A car crash?
- Yes.

410
00:29:33,194 --> 00:29:36,433
After the crash, he was laying on the road.

411
00:29:36,433 --> 00:29:38,733
He told me he was feeling dizzy.

412
00:29:38,733 --> 00:29:42,473
