434
00:31:11,413 --> 00:31:14,133
You were planning to send both of us to an early grave.

435
00:31:21,072 --> 00:31:22,691
Stay away from her!

436
00:31:22,691 --> 00:31:26,111
It's a misunderstanding. Why would I try to kill myself?

437
00:31:26,111 --> 00:31:29,111
Believe me. There are a lot of things and people in this world

438
00:31:30,152 --> 00:31:33,531
