451
00:32:30,424 --> 00:32:32,043
I'll go get changed.

452
00:32:32,043 --> 00:32:33,923
Then let's leave together.

453
00:32:33,923 --> 00:32:36,444
Sure. I'll wait for you here.

454
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:39,148
Hurry up.

455
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:49,162
