466
00:33:27,329 --> 00:33:32,789
In fact, we can discuss this and go back to following the rules we set a year ago.

467
00:33:32,789 --> 00:33:35,269
Dr. Mo said this before.

468
00:33:35,269 --> 00:33:37,969
This is the best thing about dissociative identity disorder.

469
00:33:39,170 --> 00:33:42,249
Would you have given up on Jing Zhixia if we had talked things over?

470
00:33:42,250 --> 00:33:47,029
